	<h1 class="title">意大利还造东西吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Beppe Severgnini</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-12-28 09:17:53 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/4769/medium/4769.jpg?1436652816" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


